Empath::

The boulder moves, slowly, exposing the mess it made of the femme&#39;s 
back.  &quot;Computer, damage report,&quot; Empath groans.

Her internal comp dutifully comes to life: &quot;Rear armor plating 
severely compromised.  Transformation and flight functions disabled.  
Multiple mech fluid leaks detected.&quot;

&quot;Cut off flow to damaged area.&quot;

&quot;Alert: order will severely compromise mobility.&quot;

&quot;Just do it!&quot;

&quot;Compliance.&quot;

Empath forces herself up to a sitting position as she feel her legs 
start to go numb.  Looking down the tunnel, she gasps.  &quot;There it is!&quot;

There it is indeed; a Soul Orb sitting plain as day, its soft glow 
illuminating the dead end it rests in.  There are no branches, no 
traps (unless you count the pitfall Empath just tripped), just the 
alien artifact waiting to be claimed.

